# iDream monorepo — configuration is per-package (each process loads its own
# .env from its package dir; pm2 sets cwd per app). Copy each package's
# .env.example to .env and fill in:
#
#   packages/main/.env   — main-web + gen-finalizer + main-event-consumer
#   packages/chat/.env   — chat service (web + worker), connects as chat_service role
#   packages/gen/.env    — gen-image + gen-video workers
#
# Cross-service invariants to keep consistent across the files above:
#   - REDIS_URL / *_REDIS_URL point at the same Redis cluster
#   - main.CHAT_BFF_SIGNING_SECRET == chat.CHAT_BFF_SIGNING_SECRET
#   - main.CHAT_SERVICE_URL points at chat's CHAT_PORT
#   - chat.CHAT_DATABASE_URL uses the chat_service Postgres role (db/sql/*.sql)
#
# Start everything with:  pnpm pm2:start   (see ecosystem.config.js)
